Author: MedAI Network
Title: [ANN] [MedNetwork] 🏥🏥 Next Generation AI Enabled Medical Imaging Platform 🏥🏥
Body: MedNetwork  The first AI enabled medical imaging platform on the blockchain   WEBSITE |ANNOUNCEMENT |WHITEPAPER | TWITTER | TELEGRAM | BLOG | DAPP DEMO    MedNetwork is the first Artificial Intelligence (AI) enabled medical imaging storage platform on the blockchain. The service provides low-cost, secure and distributed medical image storage with integrated AI capabilities for interpretation and diagnosis through a telemedicine overlay. Launched in January 2018, the platform is currently live with medical imaging companies and healthcare providers in the U.S., India, Rwanda and Singapore.   With a global footprint, MedNetwork is backed by Mercatus Capital in Singapore and plans to continue deploying services globally to bridge the gap between medical imaging and AI. The founding team has backgrounds building medical imaging provider companies, teleradiology, medical image networking, PACS and AI companies.   MedNetwork currently has an alpha release developed using IPFS for distributed medical image storage and an Ethereum-based Dapp for telemedicine with integrated AI diagnostics. We are happy to provide any user with an account for this private alpha release. Based on our product roadmap, we expect to launch the public beta release by the end of March 2018. This app demonstrates the integration of the teleradiology platform with AI diagnostics overlayed on the storage solution.   The core driving principle behind the MedNetwork is that technology and geography should no longer be a barrier to providing patients the optimal care. With the explosive growth and dependence on medical imaging for quantitative level diagnosis across the medical spectrum, we believe that physicians + AI + Dapps offers an opportunity to provide affordable telediagnostics and care to patients globally.  White Paper http://MedAI.click/whitepaper  One Pager http://MedAI.click/onepager  FAQ http://MedAI.click/faq  Product Roadmap http://MedAI.click/roadmap  Blog  MedNetwork — Medical Imaging on the Blockchain https://medium.com/@MedAINetwork/medical-imaging-on-the-blockchain-the-first-imaging-telemedicine-company-on-the-blockchain-6b00ade89e29  MedNetwork — Dapp Walkthrough https://medium.com/@MedAINetwork/medai-network-dapp-walkthrough-80cbaa91c240  3 ways AI and Blockchain will transform telemedicine https://medium.com/@MedAINetwork/medai-network-telemedicine-dapp-c08b59509297  Social Website   http://www.mednetwork.io Blog:      https://medium.com/@MedAINetwork/ Twitter:   https://twitter.com/MedAINetwork Linkedin:   https://www.linkedin.com/company/27246112/ Telegram:   https://t.me/MedNetwork Bounty :        http://www.mednetwork.io/bounty

Author: MedAI Network
Title: [ANN] [MedNetwork] 🏥🏥 Next Generation AI Enabled Medical Imaging Platform 🏥🏥
Body: Details Overview  Total token supply: 500 million Hard cap (including pre-sale stage): $34,500,000 Soft cap: $4,100,000 Initial price: 1 MedAI Token = $0.10 Type: ERC-20 Currencies accepted: USD, SGD, ETH, BTC Minimum ETH purchase: None Minimum wire purchase: $1000 USD Pre-sale dates: May 1-31 Pre-sale Tokens: 50M Tokens Pre-sale discount: 20% Whitelist: yes, start date TBA KYC: basic ** To be whitelisted for the Token PreSale please email us at whitelist@medai.network with your requested investment amount ** TOKEN DISTRIBUTION  Lock-up Period  Partners and Advisors - 10% of tokens will have a 1 year vesting and 3 months cliff Team and Founders - 3 years vesting with 6 months cliff  Tiers   MedAI Tokens USD Price Total Tier 1 (June 1-30) 80,000,000 0.10 8,000,000  Tier 2 (July 1-30) 60,000,000 0.15 9,000,000  Tier 3 (Aug 1-30) 30,000,000 0.20 6,000,000  Tier 4 (Sep 1-30) 30,000,000 0.25 7,500,000  Total 200,000,000  30,500,000  Unsold Tokens  75% locked for 1 year 25% locked for 2 years    Funds Raised The intent of MedAI is to raise the minimum needed funds to launch the network and platform (5.6M or soft cap). We are committed to being impeccable stewards of capital raised and to ensure that the funds are used optimally and efficiently with no waste. Each dollar raised has been earmarked for a particular need. This fundraise provides the absolute minimum required to get to our 1 year milestones and continue to develop out the platform. The remainder of the funds between the soft cap and the hard cap allows the company to scale larger faster as well as more efficiently. It allows us to deploy and develop more AI algorithms at a faster pace and provide them out to the network. It provides a longer runway and ability to fund the company over time without needing to distract the core team from more fundraising in the current pipeline and roadmap. We have outlined a detailed use of funds below.  USE OF FUNDS Initial Total Budget: $4.1MM   Development (Platform development and deployment) 25.0% Operations (QA/QI) 7.5% Infrastructure (Cloud services, ISO certification, infrastructure and equipment) 5.0% Marketing & sales (Marketing, Advertising and Promotion) 10.0% Artificial Intelligence (Algorithm Development) 22.5% Partner integrations (Platform deployment and app sales) 10% Legal (Compliance and Regulation) 5% Human resources (Growth of Machine Learning teams) 15.0%
